---
description: Never attribute commits/PRs to Cursor Agent (no Co-authored-by / Made-with trailers)
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Cursor commit attribution

- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor`, `Co-authored-by: Cursor Agent`, or any `*@cursor.com` / `*@cursor.so` trailer to commits.
- Never add `Made-with: Cursor` (or similar) trailers to commit messages or PR bodies.
- When creating commits or PRs, use only the user's git identity; do not invent co-authors for the agent.
